OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FFiona Harvey has accused the streaming
OL,7,Fplatform of defamation, intentional
OL,8,Finfliction of emotional distress,
OL,9,Fnegligence, gross negligence, and
OL,10,Fviolations of her right of publicity
OL,11,Fin the lawsuit filed at the
OL,12,FCalifornian federal court.
OL,14,FIt follows her claim to be the person
OL,15,Fthe character Martha Scott is based
OL,16,Fon, who stalks Gadd's character Donny
OL,17,FDunn after he serves her a free cup of
OL,18,Ftea in the pub where he works.
