OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FThe show is said to reflect the real-
OL,7,Flife experiences of comedian and
OL,8,Fwriter Gadd. He asked viewers not to
OL,9,Fspeculate over the real people who
OL,10,Finspired the series.
OL,12,FIn the new lawsuit, Harvey has accused
OL,13,FNetflix of spreading "brutal lies",
OL,14,Fincluding that she is a "twice
OL,15,Fconvicted stalker who was sentenced to
OL,16,Ffive years in prison".
OL,18,F"Defendants told these lies, and never
OL,19,Fstopped, because it was a better story
OL,20,Fthan the truth, and better stories
OL,21,Fmade money," it states.
