OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,F"As a result of defendants' lies,
OL,7,Fmalfeasance and utterly reckless
OL,8,Fmisconduct, Harvey's life had been
OL,9,Fruined."
OL,11,FThe court documents allege Netflix
OL,12,F"did literally nothing" to confirm
OL,13,Fthat the story represented was true,
OL,14,Fstating that "Harvey has never been
OL,15,Fconvicted of any crime and has never
OL,16,Fbeen to prison".
OL,18,FA statement from Netflix said: "We
OL,19,Fintend to defend this matter
OL,20,Fvigorously and to stand by Richard
OL,21,FGadd's right to tell his story."
